description:
Count Alfred von Lansberg was an Imperial high noble who became a military officer in the http://anidb.net/ch6230 [Lippstadt League] during the Imperial Civil War, and later took part in a Fezzani-conceived plot to kidnap Kaiser http://anidb.net/ch225 [Erwin Josef II], becoming his unofficial caretaker.
Source: Gineipaedia
name: Alfred von Lansberg
